{"id": 2062, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得在建立自己的家庭之前，需要完成哪些“先导任务”？", "description": "不考虑“先要有个对象”的问题，你觉得成家之前还需要完成哪些事情？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2857, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171212172206JDlaONCH1tTgcvIo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 255488, "content": "修身：减肥，读书，看剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 255744, "content": "有房！有车！就行！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219698}, {"id": 255489, "content": "先要有爱情?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218111}, {"id": 255490, "content": "学会负责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119768}, {"id": 255746, "content": "在哪里生活？北上广，二线还是家乡，这直接决定了能在哪里找老婆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117070}, {"id": 255491, "content": "稳定的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218988}, {"id": 255747, "content": "先存钱，提升自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219712}, {"id": 255492, "content": "有钱，有爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027663}, {"id": 255748, "content": "自己觉得真的想组建家庭啦，而不是在各方压力下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915794}, {"id": 255749, "content": "经济独立，父母能够安稳，自己的精神方面有所提升，还有各种，什么有车有房。\n\n综上所述，在遇见一个对的人时都成幻影，勇敢爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219716}, {"id": 258053, "content": "独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229756}, {"id": 255494, "content": "找到自己的意义", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218308}, {"id": 256262, "content": "有一个好的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221538}, {"id": 255495, "content": "至少应该自己知道这一天天过的都是为什么！要有自己立足于社会的技能！能够有能力担当起家庭的责任！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033904}, {"id": 255751, "content": "各方面独立，然后尝鲜尝得差不多的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185852}, {"id": 255496, "content": "先找到一个合适的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784882}, {"id": 255497, "content": "心智成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216852}, {"id": 256265, "content": "想明白自己要过什么样的生活，要同什么样的人过活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221455}, {"id": 255498, "content": "想要安定", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024790}, {"id": 255754, "content": "拥有属于自己的感情与思想；\n感情→根本.\n思想→基础.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033741}, {"id": 255499, "content": "接纳彼此的家庭，能相处融洽互相认可，规划有TA的未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747017}, {"id": 255500, "content": "一套自己的房子和能够当大人的意识", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219020}, {"id": 255756, "content": "经济独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194489}, {"id": 255501, "content": "自己要先长大吧，至少知道该怎么照顾人", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219021}, {"id": 255757, "content": "好想给心情放个假", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014485}, {"id": 255502, "content": "房，车，钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165803}, {"id": 255758, "content": "弄清楚自己的方向 ！ 一起努力！不然会很无趣！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946264}, {"id": 256270, "content": "经济独立心智成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221561}, {"id": 255503, "content": "经济独立\n人格独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219022}, {"id": 255759, "content": "有房有车有存款、还有一个健康的身体", "image": "img/option/option/20171222103411nXs1EkHKO3Fcr7T0.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013301}, {"id": 255504, "content": "先立业", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216851}, {"id": 255505, "content": "有钱有爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219025}, {"id": 256273, "content": "能够活成更好的自己，也有分开的底气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221574}, {"id": 258321, "content": "先减个肥\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151928}, {"id": 255506, "content": "准备自己，婚后怎样共同使一个大家庭越来越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192050}, {"id": 255507, "content": "先做最好的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964351}, {"id": 255508, "content": "先学会如何更好的爱自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219035}, {"id": 255509, "content": "钱啊，钱啊，钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219037}, {"id": 255765, "content": "自己得先活好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219777}, {"id": 255766, "content": "三观正，别祸害另一半和将来的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448499}, {"id": 255511, "content": "结婚钱的百分之七十要先赚好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145289}, {"id": 255767, "content": "明白生活是很实际的，绝不因你的想象和绝望而有所改变", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737792}, {"id": 255513, "content": "双方对建立家庭的动机一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217446}, {"id": 261145, "content": "跟他结婚后每天的日子过成什么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330251}, {"id": 255514, "content": "首先得要国家允许同性恋婚姻才行", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183306}, {"id": 256026, "content": "自己先活明白", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197507}, {"id": 258842, "content": "爱几个人渣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230890}, {"id": 255515, "content": "精神独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043565}, {"id": 256028, "content": "自己想要什么样的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220663}, {"id": 255517, "content": "能够独立生活就可以吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043565}]}